OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMarks & Spencer shifts from
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftown centres as online     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsales grow                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Marks & Spencer says it is moving away 
OL,6, from town centres, as it saw online    
OL,7, sales for clothes and homeware jump.   
OL,9,FThe chain said the shift to online     
OL,10,Fshopping during the pandemic had       
OL,11,F"increased the imperative" to reduce   
OL,12,Fits clothing and home trading space.   
OL,14,FMany town centres had "lost impetus"   
OL,15,Fdue to "failed local authority or      
OL,16,Fgovernment policy", M&S said.          
OL,18,FIt said it was now relocating some     
OL,19,Fshops from older, multi-floor buildings
OL,20,Fwith poor access and parking.          
